title: Trades That Make Sense
itunes:title: Trades That Make Sense
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Colleen Wolfe – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including the Zeke Elliott appeal, Chargers tattoos and Patriot Coach Bill Belichick’s refusal to mention the Jets name. Spoiler Alert: Hard Knocks Episode 2 included here.
